column1: Safety net results at each time_stamp. Each row has 2*num_agents elements. The data is formatted as follows: outside_check1, intersection_check1, outside_check2, intersection_check2, ... outside_checkN, intersection_checkN where N is the number of robots. outside_check == 1 --> agents outside flyable region. outside_check == 0 --> agents inside flyable region. intersection_check == 1 --> agent intersects with another agent. intersection_check == 0 --> agent does not intersect with other agents
